<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>PuzzleFight</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='navbar'>
      <div class='dropdown dropdown-left'>
        Instructions
        <div class='dropdown-content'>
          <p/>
          Ready to outsmart your friends? Pick a level, then double-click 'Start'. Use the keyboard
          to move the yellow piece around the board. Your goal is to capture all of the blue pieces in as 
          few moves as possible. But tread thoughtfully: accidentally capture a red piece, and your 
          score will increase by a random number between 2 and 5. Click 'Start' again at any time to 
          randomize the puzzle. The possibilies - and the possible strategies - are endless
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1 class='logoBar'>PuzzleFight</h1>
      <div class='dropdown dropdown-right'>
        <% if user_signed_in? %>  
          Hello, <%= current_user.username %>
        <% else %>
          Register
        <% end %>
        <div class='dropdown-content'>  
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <ul><%= link_to 'Update Account', edit_user_registration_path, method: :get %></ul>
            <ul><%= link_to 'Sign Out', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %></ul>
          <% else %>
            <ul><%= link_to 'Sign In', new_user_session_path %></ul>
            <ul><%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path %></ul>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>    
    </div>
    <%= yield %>
  </body>
</html>
